&lt;p&gt;Lonely Planet has been inspiring wanderlust for over 50 years, and we&#39;re looking for a talented Book Designer to help shape the next chapter. You&#39;ll join our Inspiration and Gift print publishing team to design and art direct beautifully crafted adult nonfiction trade books and print products that reach travel lovers all over the world. This is a rare opportunity to work on commercially distributed titles at a globally iconic travel brand — bringing together inspired visual storytelling and smart information design in every spread. If you live and breathe books, geek out over typography, and believe great design can make someone book a flight, we want to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
