&lt;p&gt;The Red Ventures Home Client Services group is looking for a talented Data Engineering Manager to join our team! As a Data Engineering Manager at Red Ventures, you will have the opportunity to build technology that drives real value for the users of our products all aimed at helping people choose best possible services/products for them. You will lead a team tasked with designing, developing, testing, and maintaining big data pipelines to create a foundation that powers our business analytics and machine learning efforts to drive our vision! This role partners closely with external clients, and we are looking for someone who builds trust quickly, communicates with clarity at every level, and represents the team with confidence in high-stakes conversations.&lt;/p&gt;
