&lt;li&gt;4+ years of hands-on experience with Databricks and the ability to architect solutions within the platform, including Unity Catalog, Delta Lake, and workflow orchestration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4+ years of experience working on cloud technologies; AWS preferred but welcome candidates with Azure or GCP experience.&lt;/li&gt;
