&lt;li&gt;Collaborate effectively with cross-functional teams such as Talent Management, Learning &amp;amp; Development, and Recruiting to implement people strategies that drive both business performance and employee engagement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as owner for your teams on key talent processes with business teams including performance review, talent calibrations, talent planning, and leadership development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coach first level managers through day-to-day performance management to ensure employees are receiving coaching and feedback and career development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement, maintain the integrity of, and inform change to HR policies and practices through continuous interaction with employees and teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
