&lt;li&gt;Troubleshoot and resolve complex technical problems with minimal supervision, including responding to monitoring alerts and taking appropriate action&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support identity and access management (provisioning, deprovisioning, access reviews across platforms like Okta), network troubleshooting (connectivity, DNS, VPN), and collaboration tooling (Microsoft 365, Teams, Zoom, and related integrations)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with asset management, including device tracking, hardware lifecycle, inventory accuracy, and shipping/receiving of equipment as needed&lt;/li&gt;
