&lt;li&gt;Analyze recurring tickets and incidents to identify workflow gaps and develop scalable solutions, including automation opportunities, that reduce repetitive work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to the training and continuous improvement of our AI Service Agent (Freddy), including reviewing AI-generated responses for accuracy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate on cross-functional IT projects, own assigned tasks and projects from start to finish, and mentor teammates to support skill development and team success&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We’re Looking For:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
