&lt;li&gt;Build and develop strategic, customized media plans in response to RFPs and client requests.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work cross-functionally to support the pre-sale to post-sale transition process by ensuring accurate documentation, pricing plan reviews, and communication with internal stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in the creation and refinement of sales materials including pitch decks and kick off call decks.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze audience, competitive, and performance data to inform media planning decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain accurate documentation of plans, budgets, and revisions. Optimize sales cycle and report data to senior leadership.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
