&lt;li&gt;Strong external/client-facing experience with the ability to build and maintain relationships, communicate clearly and professionally, anticipate client needs, present strategies and results, and represent the team with a solutions-oriented approach.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with emerging ad tech trends — from retail media networks to AI-driven targeting and privacy-first strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in Excel, PowerPoint, and Google Workspace products; familiarity with media math and forecasting. Experience with Boostr is a plus but not required.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analytical mindset paired with exceptional storytelling skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
